title: Pink Floyd - Amsterdam Rock Circus
description:
Pink Floyd.

The Complete Amsterdam Rock Circus. 


This has to be one of the most interesting video's of the Floyd.
Filmed on a hand held camera in black and white with lots of camera shake!
Its a pure audiance view of the Floyd in the 70's.
Its a must for all Floyd fans.





1. Atom Heart Mother: The last "Ever" live perfomance.

2. Careful With That Axe Eugene.

3. A Saucerful Of Secrets.


37min.
